# Frontend role

**May edit:** `apps/client/`, `apps/admin/`, `packages/ui/src/`

**May not edit:** `apps/api/`, `packages/contracts/`

**Must:** Zustand for client state, `@chronomint/ui` primitives, `@chronomint/web-shared` for shared app code, and tests with every feature (`packages/ui` → `*.spec.tsx`, admin/client `features/` → Playwright e2e or unit spec)
